sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Intel ( INTC ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.9%.
Year to date, Intel has lost about 4.5% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Chevron ( CVX ), trading down 1.5%.
Chevron is lower by about 22.0% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Exxon Mobil ( XOM ), trading down 1.2%, and Home Depot ( HD ), trading up 1.8% on the day.
